<script>
     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
</script><p>The Tiv people belong to a minor ethnic group in Nigeria numbering about six million. They have a rich history associated with their existence. The culture and tradition of the Tiv people is one that is envied by many who come in contact with them.</p>
<h2></h2>
<h2>Quick Fact About The Tiv People</h2>
<p>They occupy the middle belt region of Nigeria, comprising of states such As Benue, Taraba, Nassarawa and Plateau.</p><div class="t0VORxEt" style="clear:both;float:left;width:100%;margin:0 0 20px 0;"><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-9755093768544960"
     crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<!-- 2 -->
<ins class="adsbygoogle"
     style="display:block"
     data-ad-client="ca-pub-9755093768544960"
     data-ad-slot="4927364444"
     data-ad-format="auto"
     data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins>
<script>
     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
</script>

<br/>

<h2 style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #ff6600;"><strong>👉 Relocate to Canada Today!</strong></span></h2>
<strong>Live, Study and Work in Canada.</strong> No Payment is Required! Hurry Now click here to Apply >> <a href="https://infoguidenigeria.com/tie-travel/immigrate-to-canada/" target="_blank"><strong>Immigrate to Canada</strong></a>

<br/>


</div>
<p>They can also be found in Cameroun.</p>
<p>They are predominantly Christians although Islam is also practiced among them.</p><div class="HoeIzLdL" style="clear:both;float:left;width:100%;margin:0 0 20px 0;"><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-9755093768544960"
     crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<!-- 4 -->
<ins class="adsbygoogle"
     style="display:block"
     data-ad-client="ca-pub-9755093768544960"
     data-ad-slot="8693055927"
     data-ad-format="auto"
     data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins>
<script>
     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
</script></div>
<p>They are great farmers producing crops such as yam, cassava, maize, mellon etc</p>
<p>Tiv land stretches from Agede in Benue in the south east, Iyala, Gekem and Obudu in Cross River, Chambam and Junkun of Taraba in the northeast and Idoma of Benue in the south.</p><div class="kaGa2N1g" style="clear:both;float:left;width:100%;margin:0 0 20px 0;"><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-9755093768544960"
     crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<!-- 6 -->
<ins class="adsbygoogle"
     style="display:block"
     data-ad-client="ca-pub-9755093768544960"
     data-ad-slot="8681463542"
     data-ad-format="auto"
     data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins>
<script>
     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
</script></div>
<p>&nbsp;</p><div class="stream-item stream-item-in-post stream-item-inline-post alignleft"><div class="stream-item-size" style=""><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-9755093768544960"
     crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
