<h2>History of the Tiv People</h2>
<p>Tiv became known to the outside world during an expedition lead by Lieutenant-Colonel Huge Trenchard from 1907 to 1908.</p>				<div id="inline-related-post" class="mag-box mini-posts-box content-only">
