<p>Tiv people descended from a man known to many as Takurudu, Shon, Gbe,Awanje And Karagbe. He was regarded as the founding father of Tiv.</p>
<p>He gave birth to two children Ichongoa and Ipsu. Ichongo gave birth to Gondo, Ikyura, Nongo, Ihar, Mase and Turan,while Ipusu gave birth to Shitire, Kum, Kpar.</p><div class="ztkNG7Wk" style="clear:both;float:left;width:100%;margin:0 0 20px 0;"><h2 style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #ff6600;"><strong>👉 Relocate to Canada Today!</strong></span></h2>
