<p>These ten children are the direct descendants of the Tiv people. According to its history, Tiv first settled in Swerm but due to overpopulation they spread from the hills of the south eastern Tivland to<br />
the middle belt region.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p><div class="O8ZKV91R" style="clear:both;float:left;width:100%;margin:0 0 20px 0;"><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-9755093768544960"
