					<div class="comment-metadata">
						<a href="https://infoguidenigeria.com/the-tiv-people/#comment-12763"><time datetime="2017-01-29T15:12:24+01:00">January 29, 2017 at 3:12 pm</time></a>					</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

									</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Mwuese angbian u a nger kwagh sha mlu u tyo i Tiv la. Mumbur ayange ker jime kpee nahan angbianev asev mba kpishi wa gomneti u Benue  kwagh er : man i tesen zwa u tyoo ne ker makeranta i kiriki er primary man secondary nahan. kpa zan zan nyian mba  a fatyo i er kwagh  ne ga. A er nan ve ior asev vea fa kwagh u tyoo tsembelee? Tiv mba ve lu ker atotyev  ka vea nenge a or zwa ve kpa mba tesen kyav er ve mba angbianev ga. Ne mba  ne gande yol yo  sor nen tar Tiv  kpa nea fatyo ga yo se mba kiriki se son Aondo una wase se yo, se sor tar wase. Msugh tyo.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

				<div class="reply"><a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-12763' data-commentid="12763" data-postid="2872" data-belowelement="div-comment-12763" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Gema Terhemba Thaddeus" aria-label='Reply to Gema Terhemba Thaddeus'>Reply</a></div>			</article><!-- .comment-body -->
		</li><!-- #comment-## -->
